data.description: DO NOT MISS THIS OPPORTUNITY.   Bring your horses/animals, many possibilities to own over 6 rolling acres or subdivide and build additional house or sell.  Located in NEW Liberty Creek school zone, Possible mini farm with Gatlinburg like views in highly desirable Sumner county area. Easy access to bypass, close to shopping, downtown Nashville, hospital, upcoming Facebook center, Costco and so much more. Home is over 1350 Sq. ft. , 3bed, 2ba w/ covered front and back porches.  Newer water heater, beautiful pond, large barn w/ multiple stalls, barn rood has been reinforced but interior needs work.  Milk shed currently used for storage, back of the property is fully fenced in, nice large dog house. Lots of potential!
